        <title type="html"><![CDATA[shell if]]></title>
        <id>https://www.thiswind.work/post/shell-if</id>
        <link href="https://www.thiswind.work/post/shell-if">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-19T09:26:31.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code class="language-bash">if test -f abc.txt; then
    ls -l abc.txt
fi
</code></pre>
