    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[shell test not]]></title>
        <id>https://www.thiswind.work/post/shell-test-not</id>
        <link href="https://www.thiswind.work/post/shell-test-not">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-19T09:25:23.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The test command syntax is as follows:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">! expression
</code></pre>
<p>OR</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">[ ! expression ]
</code></pre>
<p>OR</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">if test ! condition
then
     command1
     command2
fi
if [ ! condition ]
then
     command1
     command2
fi
</code></pre>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The test command syntax is as follows:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">! expression
