<pre><code class="language-bash">[ ! expression ]
</code></pre>
<p>OR</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">if test ! condition
then
     command1
     command2
fi
if [ ! condition ]
then
     command1
     command2
fi
</code></pre>
]]></content>
