    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[如何用`cut`命令找到最后一个字段]]></title>
        <id>https://www.thiswind.work/post/ru-he-yong-cutming-ling-zhao-dao-zui-hou-yi-ge-zi-duan</id>
        <link href="https://www.thiswind.work/post/ru-he-yong-cutming-ling-zhao-dao-zui-hou-yi-ge-zi-duan">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-19T07:04:55.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code class="language-bash">pwd | rev | cut -d &quot;/&quot; -f 1 | rev
</code></pre>
<p>原理：</p>
<ol>
<li>逆向</li>
<li>切分，找到第一项</li>
<li>逆向，还原</li>
</ol>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code class="language-bash">pwd | rev | cut -d &quot;/&quot; -f 1 | rev
</code></pre>
<p>原理：</p>
<ol>
<li>逆向</li>
<li>切分，找到第一项</li>
<li>逆向，还原</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
