        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Quote this to prevent word splitting]]></title>
        <id>https://www.thiswind.work/post/quote-this-to-prevent-word-splitting</id>
        <link href="https://www.thiswind.work/post/quote-this-to-prevent-word-splitting">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-11-15T14:08:05.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Problematic code:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">ls -l $(getfilename)
</code></pre>
<p>Correct code:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">ls -l &quot;$(getfilename)&quot;
</code></pre>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Problematic code:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">ls -l $(getfilename)
</code></pre>
<p>Correct code:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash">ls -l &quot;$(getfilename)&quot;
</code></pre>
]]></content>
    </entry>
